ISLAMABAD, May 24 (APP): Minister for Narcotic Control Ijaz Ahmed Shah on Monday expressed grief and sorrow over the death of Liaquat Khan, brother of Minister for Aviation Ghulam Sarwar Khan.
In his condolence message, he prayed for the departed soul and commiserated with the bereaved family.
